<br>
Yes, chanters and druids could solo for good exp with it, and?  Druids have always been able to solo for better exp than a warrior.  Warriors don't solo well, that doesn't mean classes that can solo should be nerfed.<br>
<br>
I think they should have changed the mobs instead of the spell.  Make it impossible to charm the mobs that are used for soloing named mobs that can drop runes, etc.  Why destroy an ability that was useful just because it can be used to get better exp than we can get solo, or it can be used situationally to get nice loot.  Fix the situations, change mobs around, don't destroy part of a class.<br>
<br>
